selectionPosition 
Game: Armed Assault (1.00) 
Description: Search for selection in the object model (first in the memory level 
, then in geometry LODs, then in roadway LOD [VBS2 only]). 
Returns position in model space. In A1 it returns the initial position 
 of the selection, in A2 and VBS2 it returns the current position 
 of the selection (e.g. when it is animated). 
If a selection does not exist [0,0,0] is returned.  
Syntax:  
 object selectionPosition selectionName 
Parameters: 
object: Object 
selectionName: String 
Return Value: 
 Array